column5: Happy New Year everyone! I'm planning a small fishing trip to Haliburton in June. A friend of mine told me Little Kennisis Lake is a pretty good. Have anyone fish there before? What other species are there? Any public launch? Any information will be greatly appreciated. Cheers,
I can’t help you on species or techniques, But there is a Gravel launch to both lakes
Thank you very much for the info.
Just ordered a copy of the map! Thanks again.
not sure if this will work  http://fishing-app.gpsnauticalcharts.com/i-boating-fishing-web-app/fishing-marine-charts-navigation.html?title=Ontario+Lakes+boating+app#14.08/45.2510/-78.5832
Nice! This map works. Thanks a lot. I've ordered a copy following BillM's link last week. Should be getting it soon. Thanks again!
